{"tid":1425862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如何使用麻布袋方法","createTime":"2019-08-06T22:18:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T01:57:02.000Z","uid":58841,"like":117,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"550700ab7c5a1820d20c7d6dabc0bbbc9f46b216","tid":1425862,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T22:18:53.000Z","msg":"可組4-6人團/最好有成班街坊<br />\n1.觀察1-2個禮拜追蹤狗隻作息 例如咩時間出門口，咩時間返屋企<br />\n2.留意狗隻表情同步伐，越攰就反應越遲鈍<br />\n3.留意附近CCTV位置，做野個陣搵人遮住鏡頭，一定有死角位<br />\n4.建議夜晚做野<br />\n5.如果人數眾多可以玩人海戰術，到時成班人衝上去無人知邊個郁手<br />\n6.人數少就要睇準時機，跟蹤個陣保持距離，通常扮玩電話聽歌最安全<br />\n<br />\n利申：發夢夢到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3273d2e37131d7346a4c3507af634d56460d4d05","tid":1425862,"uid":237838,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T22:31:36.000Z","msg":"[找亮點]到底係狗扮暴徒定有黑社會扮狗？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1425838\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1425838</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n同浸大學生會會長有關！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幫推一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07d013412e8010730e2ff725f5b9aac32b72c452","tid":1425862,"uid":301255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T22:33:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9a918519279f59695d3910480d2a2c89840dc2f3","tid":1425862,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T22:34:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05d4c6718f34bfe6dbd13761283a62ce7fc4d186","tid":1425862,"uid":9315,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T22:35:05.000Z","msg":"小心皮屑/汗 &amp; 口水等體液/衣物纖維/鞋印/指模會留係現場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddb42f41f03012e31b172d72eea300784d9b409a","tid":1425862,"uid":58841,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05d4c6718f34bfe6dbd13761283a62ce7fc4d186","tid":1425862,"uid":9315,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T22:35:05.000Z","msg":"小心皮屑/汗 &amp; 口水等體液/衣物纖維/鞋印/指模會留係現場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T22:37:45.000Z","msg":"1.戴手套同著鞋套<br />\n2.做完野要睇下附近有冇頭髮留係現場"},{"pid":"9ac4559c44d4d5a13541fd3b8d634a28245470ee","tid":1425862,"uid":105344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T22:38:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4bf3a50a699912d024a4c1a68ef29af41eca6b6d","tid":1425862,"uid":58841,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T22:41:21.000Z","msg":"3.唔好係現場見血，佢有技術好似可以見到留過既血跡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4.最好附近有垃圾場，通常無乜CCTV係度，垃圾場位置多數係大廈後門"},{"pid":"e28f346d408a2d05eb709e7264c31697bdbe421b","tid":1425862,"uid":58841,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T22:46:28.000Z","msg":"5.關於消滅用過既野，搵野剪碎佢，然後DUM係唔同地方，DUM同一個地方好易砌返出黎<br />\n6.唔需要帶咩架餐，基本上擺佢係垃圾場臭到佢仆街已經夠哂折磨，當然最好斷一兩隻手，同埋唔好綁太實等佢死唔去先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f313cc29b9f00ea89dced7db5603ec9e99b6bbdd","tid":1425862,"uid":58841,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T22:54:39.000Z","msg":"點樣辨認狗隻：<br />\n而家單野搞到咁大，基本上狗隻不論返屋企定返工都一定疑神疑鬼<br />\n例如玩電話個陣好多時隻手指無乜點郁過<br />\n四周圍望<br />\n步伐係有少少唔自然<br />\n扮鎮定<br />\n<br />\n追蹤對方個陣唔好長期留係同一個位置，會俾人跟到<br />\n最好留係多人地方，例如餐廳/地鐵站，唔一定守係佢屋企出面"},{"pid":"13f41b425d951c1a3cab7ec7200ecf2c9b609936","tid":1425862,"uid":111253,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T22:57:36.000Z","msg":"狗隻精神長期受壓，圓嘅範圍應該得半徑2米"},{"pid":"a12950264f551ead2d88fa05eb5030df2626bf24","tid":1425862,"uid":58841,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T23:01:58.000Z","msg":"基本上做得狗隻都一定有潛意識動作<br />\n即係職業病<br />\n例如無意識將手擺側腰（拔槍/拎棍姿勢）<br />\n翹手<br />\n表面惡形惡勢 但係其實好撚呆<br />\n做得狗係有樣睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f96b218f8d26c817e6f9b738089f747ec548ea85","tid":1425862,"uid":260201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T23:05:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dad68637e436930859b2c63d1ded78b5a5071ae5","tid":1425862,"uid":58841,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T23:05:35.000Z","msg":"有條撚樣逐條負皮我COMMENT<br />\n你班狗隻神憎鬼厭<br />\n小心出出下街俾人掟左落垃圾場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"701124359ea3c4862753a3db7bc2d252e12615c4","tid":1425862,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T23:09:51.000Z","msg":"好多休班警有槍"},{"pid":"f53cc8190dbf7a97f08e33a962af07b7a6a40d4d","tid":1425862,"uid":251083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T23:10:55.000Z","msg":"佢哋好驚有陌生人係狗宿舍附近散步，并派不少狗力巡邏，證明好緊張果啲地方，食飽飯去散步喇"},{"pid":"d46c288f53ab4420c4c1702bd82de41f719523f1","tid":1425862,"uid":293619,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T23:10:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P2BO3Mq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP2BO3Mq.jpg&h=409baf02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ebe1EjM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Febe1EjM.jpg&h=693ca5af&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"47721c09a3ed4d36d68313085905f5beab1d2a36","tid":1425862,"uid":58841,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T23:12:45.000Z","msg":"A: 0700-1545 <br />\nB: 1500-2345 <br />\nC: 2300-0745"},{"pid":"4872d1036b6e913e7b31b1557da7ec6a323f9900","tid":1425862,"uid":53870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T23:13:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">麻包袋</span></span>"},{"pid":"146420c9e16fef89e6825be09e9f8d4b1527ba38","tid":1425862,"uid":43553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T23:15:13.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"abba48de48da6c9d742fd2259e0eced5cc2e73cf","tid":1425862,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47721c09a3ed4d36d68313085905f5beab1d2a36","tid":1425862,"uid":58841,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T23:12:45.000Z","msg":"A: 0700-1545 <br />\nB: 1500-2345 <br />\nC: 2300-0745"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T23:15:54.000Z","msg":"狗隻更表"},{"pid":"9671be9125051c1f9faf39263c6bb571d6be2dd6","tid":1425862,"uid":58841,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T23:17:39.000Z","msg":"狗隻弱點一定係腳度<br />\n因為呢班狗好多時只會操上身，下身其實好撚廢<br />\n要捉狗瞄後腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9fc6c7086751bcd27f532546dad41a45223a4b9","tid":1425862,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T23:19:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e33112393a6605af960d30097fe60dc8169e1196","tid":1425862,"uid":68220,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ddb42f41f03012e31b172d72eea300784d9b409a","tid":1425862,"uid":58841,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05d4c6718f34bfe6dbd13761283a62ce7fc4d186","tid":1425862,"uid":9315,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T22:35:05.000Z","msg":"小心皮屑/汗 &amp; 口水等體液/衣物纖維/鞋印/指模會留係現場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T22:37:45.000Z","msg":"1.戴手套同著鞋套<br />\n2.做完野要睇下附近有冇頭髮留係現場"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T23:20:25.000Z","msg":"搜證通常會睇cctv搵耳仔/眉毛/鞋印"},{"pid":"4af20ccba8ae6258952818bd0e76d8187b53473f","tid":1425862,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e33112393a6605af960d3